{"data":[{"date":"13:13 30/06","title":"HLV Hierro ch\u1ed1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/hlv-hierro-chot-5-cau-thu-tay-ban-nha-da-luan-luu-11m.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u00f2 t\u00f3t chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng thua v\u1edbi Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. </h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Hierro cho c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u00a0 t\u1eadp s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Moscow.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd AS, Hierro c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103m c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch trong lo\u1ea1t \"\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\" n\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i sau 120 ph\u00fat. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd l\u00e0 David Silva. Ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00fat sau anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Diego Costa, Isco v\u00e0 Sergio Busquets. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n, l\u00e0 Andres Iniesta.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hierro ch\u1ed1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hierro ch\u1ed1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/tbn-3292-1530291497.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng d\u00f9 g\u1eb7p Nga - \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u01b0a th\u00edch t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u1ea2nh: AS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Hierro c\u0169ng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, n\u01a1i \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng quy\u1ec1n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 theo lu\u1eadt m\u1edbi m\u00e0 FIFA \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady theo t\u1edd Marca (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ea1 Nga trong hai hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n \u201cLa Roja\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u1ee9ng minh Nga v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup 2018 thua c\u1ea3 ba l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i l\u1edbn. \u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a 3-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSergio Ramos ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hierro tin t\u01b0\u1edfng giao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nga v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 21h ng\u00e0y 1/7, theo gi\u1edd H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"747","checkdouble":"189989"},{"date":"14:12 30/06","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tien-dao-mbappe-dung-tien-thuong-tai-world-cup-2018-de-lam-tu-thien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nB\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u00ec 4 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo. Anh l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n, ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 im ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady. thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Fernando Santos m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n CR7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay, \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft m\u1edbi gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Santos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi Uruguay c\u00e2u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 Luis Suarez hay Edinson Cavani. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" title=\"BDN vs Iran Ronaldo di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-sau-tran-dau-bdn-11-iran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd thua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng su\u1ed1t 12 n\u0103m, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng v\u0169 kh\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c thua.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf t\u1eebng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h \u0111\u00eam nay (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin xung quanh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7): Tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean khai h\u1ecfa nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\">Suarez nh\u1eafn Ronaldo: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nLuis Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona nh\u1eafn Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\">Uruguay kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nSebastian Coates ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o CR7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"746","checkdouble":"189990"},{"date":"15:10 30/06","title":"\"VAR \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/var-dang-phat-huy-hieu-qua-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (FIFA) kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111ang h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">ESPN \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1eeba qua, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u1ee6y ban Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i FIFA Pierluigi Collina v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 xem l\u1ea1i di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 48 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 335 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1edfi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng ngh\u00ea VAR h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 14 l\u1ea7n, t\u0103ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c trong c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb 95% l\u00ean 99,3%. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i 100%. Tuy nhi\u00ean, 99,3% l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. C\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb VAR\u201d, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Collina l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh VAR \u0111ang t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/cthoyvartrialperiodcouldbedelayedbeyond2018worldcup20171005.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">FIFA kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh VAR \u0111ang h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb FIFA cho th\u1ea5y trung b\u00ecnh c\u00f3 4 pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u1edf m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng so v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 (3 th\u1ebb). D\u00f9 v\u1eady, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng penalty t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 48 tr\u1eadn, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 24 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra. Con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 10 penalty \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2010 v\u00e0 World cup 2014. 24 qu\u1ea3 penalty c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a World Cup, v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 18 qu\u1ea3 penalty.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Collina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh VAR \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh v\u00e0 FIFA s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1y, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111i b\u1ed9, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR v\u1eady\u201d, \u00f4ng nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFIFA cho r\u1eb1ng VAR kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 r\u00f5 th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd trung b\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 t\u0103ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat (t\u1eeb 5 ph\u00fat l\u00ean 6 ph\u00fat).<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR\u00a0t\u1ea1i\u00a0World Cup 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-sao-trong-tai-cakir-khong-thoi-11m-cho-nigeria-du-ap-dung-var-421-189703.html\">V\u00ec sao tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cakir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i 11m cho Nigeria d\u00f9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-nuoc-anh-chui-boi-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-bo-dao-nha-421-189575.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\">Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cong-nghe-var-bat-viet-vi-ra-sao-461-189194.html\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR b\u1eaft vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb ra sao</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/var-tai-world-cup-2018-lan-ranh-giua-duoc-va-mat-466-189193.html\">VAR t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: L\u1eb1n ranh gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nghi-an-trong-tai-mat-lien-lac-var-tran-bdn-10-morocco-421-189125.html\">Nghi \u00e1n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i m\u1ea5t li\u00ean l\u1ea1c VAR tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 1-0 Morocco</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/amrabat-phat-bieu-ve-cong-nghe-var-421-189101.html\">Sao Ma R\u1ed1c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cVAR l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 d\u1ee5ng\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"745","checkdouble":"189992"},{"date":"15:17 30/06","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tien-ve-ozil-noi-gi-ve-ky-world-cup-2018-tham-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Mesut Ozil ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \"c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng\" ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 10 Mesut Oezil.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/po.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Oezil t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i khi c\u00f3 b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p chung v\u1edbi T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Recep Tayyip Erdogan. Ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Oezil l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 l\u1ea7n anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, \"Die Mannschaft\" \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u01a1n m\u01b0a \"g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1\" t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, s\u1ed1 10 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 s\u1ef1 im l\u1eb7ng. Tr\u00ean trang Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Oezil chia s\u1ebb: \"Th\u1eadt \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn khi ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi World Cup ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00fa s\u1ed1c n\u00e0y\" k\u00e8m theo hashtah #SayNoToRacism (N\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Oezil. R\u1ea5t may khi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi 2 b\u00ean x\u1ea3y ra \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"744","checkdouble":"189993"},{"date":"15:49 30/06","title":"HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: \"N\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a d\u1eabm v\u00e0o Ronaldo, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua ch\u1eafc\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hlv-bo-dao-nha-neu-dua-dam-vao-ronaldo-chung-toi-thua-chac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nB\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u00ec 4 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo. Anh l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n, ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 im ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady. thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Fernando Santos m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n CR7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay, \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft m\u1edbi gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Santos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi Uruguay c\u00e2u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 Luis Suarez hay Edinson Cavani. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" title=\"BDN vs Iran Ronaldo di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-sau-tran-dau-bdn-11-iran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd thua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng su\u1ed1t 12 n\u0103m, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng v\u0169 kh\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c thua.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf t\u1eebng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h \u0111\u00eam nay (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin xung quanh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7): Tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean khai h\u1ecfa nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\">Suarez nh\u1eafn Ronaldo: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nLuis Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona nh\u1eafn Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\">Uruguay kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nSebastian Coates ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o CR7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"743","checkdouble":"189994"},{"date":"16:02 30/06","title":"Sampaoli: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00f9 nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a Messi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/sampaoli-toi-khong-phai-bu-nhin-cua-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1, Argentina r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Sampaoli chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.\r\n</h2><h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-phap-vs-argentina-463-189998.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina 21h00 ng\u00e0y 30/6 (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSampaoli ph\u1ea3i xin ph\u00e9p Messi?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, Argentina b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. Qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u1eadp &ldquo;t\u1ed5 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1edbi Mascherano v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Jorge Sampaoli.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nigeria, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ngay-hom-nay-276-469-189725.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sampaoli th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea3i xin ph\u00e9p Messi \u0111\u1ec3 thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span> (cho Kun Aguero v\u00e0o s\u00e2n). \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f9 nh\u00ecn tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, HLV n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111ang m\u00f4 t\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Messi v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sampaoli chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p\" title=\"Sampaoli n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/sampaoli-toi-khong-phai-bu-nhin-cua-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sampaoli chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Argentina tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng v\u1eadt l\u00fd, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Argentina. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi. Nh\u01b0ng Argentina c\u0169ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy Messi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 h\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a b\u00ean n\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tinh n\u00e0y, ngo\u00e0i ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, HLV n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch xin t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, b\u1edfi \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi L\u0110B\u0110 Argentina. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Sampaoli chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Messi, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 n\u1ed9i t\u00ecnh Argentina \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m \u1ed5n, v\u00e0 h\u00e3y ch\u1edd xem m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-argentina-21h-ngay-306-khi-chua-cuu-the-da-tro-lai-421-189978.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-argentina-21h-ngay-306-khi-chua-cuu-the-da-tro-lai.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-argentina-21h-ngay-306-khi-chua-cuu-the-da-tro-lai-421-189978.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina (21h ng\u00e0y 30/6): Khi &ldquo;Ch\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i&hellip;</span><br>\r\nArgentina nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c &ldquo;Ch\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf&rdquo; tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ee7a World Cup, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi-421-189970.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-dt-phap-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-lionel-messi-421-189970.html\">Sao \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110T Ph\u00e1p Hugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina-465-189933.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/samuel-umtiti-noi-ve-messi-truoc-tran-phap-vs-argentina-465-189933.html\">Samuel Umtiti: \u0110T Argentina kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Messi</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Barcelona nay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"742","checkdouble":"189995"},{"date":"16:18 30/06","title":"HLV Uruguay: \"Ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/hlv-uruguay-chang-ai-co-the-ngan-chan-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Uruguay \u2013 HLV Tabarez chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u00f4ng coi tr\u1ecdng Ronaldo nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nUruguay kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00ec CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 Fisht, Uruguay s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Cris Ronaldo &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng theo HLV Oscar Tabarez, \u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 CR7, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Uruguay cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Uruguay s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, nh\u00ecn chung l\u00e0 v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng Ronaldo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay thang NGa 3-0\" title=\"Uruguay thang NGa 3-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Uruguay-thang-NGa-3-0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tabarez chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Godin, kh\u00f4ng ai c\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c theo t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0110T Uruguay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i coi tr\u1ecdng s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2016. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, trong 3 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau trong 12 n\u0103m qua \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean nh\u1edb Uruguay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi 3 tri\u1ec7u d\u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i 50 tri\u1ec7u. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Tabarez chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h \u0111\u00eam nay (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bo-dao-nha-neu-dua-dam-vao-ronaldo-chung-toi-thua-chac-421-189994.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hlv-bo-dao-nha-neu-dua-dam-vao-ronaldo-chung-toi-thua-chac.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bo-dao-nha-neu-dua-dam-vao-ronaldo-chung-toi-thua-chac-421-189994.html\">HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: N\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a d\u1eabm v\u00e0o Ronaldo, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua ch\u1eafc</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7): Tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean khai h\u1ecfa nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\">Suarez nh\u1eafn Ronaldo: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nLuis Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona nh\u1eafn Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"741","checkdouble":"189996"},{"date":"17:16 30/06","title":"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/chelsea-san-sang-ban-courtois-cho-real-madrid.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thibaut Courtois cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u1ee7a hai b\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Courtois mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Madrid thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u01a1i m\u00e0 v\u1ee3 c\u0169 v\u00e0 con c\u1ee7a Courtois \u0111ang sinh s\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/chelsea-san-sang-ban-courtois-cho-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Marca m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Christophe Henrotay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real. Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Chelsea c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Courtois b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gia nh\u1eadp Real. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi ph\u00eda Chelsea r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. N\u1ebfu Courtois ra \u0111i v\u00e0o n\u0103m sau, coi nh\u01b0 Chelsea ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i l\u1ed9c g\u00ec t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois c\u00f4ng khai mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u01a1i l\u1ea1i mong mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n cho c\u00e1c con trong b\u00e0i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00e1c con l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ch\u00fang trong 18 th\u00e1ng qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cG\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n video c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng quan s\u00e1t ch\u00fang l\u1edbn l\u00ean t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y th\u00ec kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. C\u00e1c con t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Real \u0111\u00e3 lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Keylor Navas. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/liverpool-va-real-nhan-tin-mung-vu-thu-mon-cua-roma-180-182742.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson</span> c\u1ee7a Roma nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u00e0 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh, Courtois l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u1ed1t, Real ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, con s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Chelsea mong mu\u1ed1n khi t\u00e2m tr\u00ed Courtois b\u00e2y gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng Courtois, Chelsea s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n th\u00e1o ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Courtois:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-len-day-cot-tinh-than-truoc-dai-chien-voi-dt-anh-421-189486.html\">Courtois l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thang-thuyet-phuc-courtois-chi-trich-panama-choi-xau-421-188881.html\">Th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, Courtois ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Panama ch\u1ec9 nh\u0103m nhe ch\u1eb7t ch\u00e9m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"740","checkdouble":"189997"},{"date":"17:00 30/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina 21h00 ng\u00e0y 30/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/30/truc-tiep-phap-vs-argentina.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ph\u00e1p v\u00f2ng 1/8 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 30/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina vs Ph\u00e1p v\u00f2ng 1/8 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 30/6.</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-phap-vs-argentina-463-189998.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP PH\u00c1P VS ARGENTINA</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"739","checkdouble":"189998"},{"date":"09:04 30/06","title":"Mesut Ozil n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c mang t\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/mesut-ozil-noi-gi-ve-cu-soc-mang-ten-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mesut Ozil ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c mang t\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T \u0111\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mesut Ozil ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Mesut-Ozil-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mesut Ozil r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n sau khi \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u0110\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 ra qu\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 2-1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-2. V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y h\u1ecd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. HLV <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-loew-van-chua-het-soc-sau-khi-tro-ve-duc-421-189971.html\" target=\"_blank\">Joachim Loew s\u1ed1c n\u1eb7ng sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMesut Ozil ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPh\u1ea3i r\u1eddi World Cup ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i \u0111au r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ebfn NHM, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, b\u1edfi v\u1eady b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Joachim Loew kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Ozil v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil that than sau tran thua Han Quoc\" title=\"Ozil th\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n sau tr\u1eadn thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/mesut-ozil-noi-gi-ve-cu-soc-mang-ten-dt-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ozil cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf World Cup 2018, Ozil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 khi ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eefa. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi 100% phong \u0111\u1ed9, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00f4i l\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e1c trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"738","checkdouble":"189981"},{"date":"09:20 30/06","title":"Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0a ra d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/16/alexis-sanchez-dua-ra-du-doan-doi-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alexis Sanchez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alexis Sanchez mu\u1ed1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, ngo\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Alexis-Sanchez-phat-bieu-ve-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez mu\u1ed1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p, Brazil, T\u00e2y Ban Nha, B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n B\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Lukaku l\u00ean ng\u00f4i c\u00f9ng B\u1ec9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tay s\u0103n b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng nhau m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sanchez th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec Chile kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac Chile gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, song s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat \u1edf\u00a0nh\u1eefng l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin sang 25/3: Sanchez tim lai niem vui o DT Chile\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 25/3: Sanchez t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui \u1edf \u0110T Chile\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/25/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-3152018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec Chile kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/alexis-alejandro-sanchez-43816.html\" target=\"_blank\">Alexis Sanchez </span>c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi Chile kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Nga v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec Chile kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1edbi Nga. V\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chile\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i, Bravo hay Vidal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb n\u1eefa, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"737","checkdouble":"189982"},{"date":"09:54 30/06","title":"Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca, nh\u01b0ng MU th\u00ec kh\u00e1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/23/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-willian-cho-barca-nhung-mu-thi-khac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u, HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Kha-nang-MU-mua-Willian-voi-gia-60-trieu-bang-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Don Ba Lon, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea. \u00d4ng Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Chelsea nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Braizl.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i MU Willian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Willian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n, theo Mirror, Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca l\u00e0 b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y khi ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n h\u1ecd ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian di bong\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Chelsea-giai-khat-chien-thang-Nuong-theo-Ao-thuat-gia-Willian-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mua Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 khi chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London m\u1edbi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra \u0111i. Hi\u1ec7n M.U v\u1eabn \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i Willian, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu Willian kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 M.U d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"736","checkdouble":"189983"},{"date":"10:08 30/06","title":"\"Mourinho s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t khi gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Fellaini\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/30/mourinho-sang-suot-khi-giu-chan-fellaini.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fellaini</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marouane Fellaini tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi khai th\u00e1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 7 n\u0103m nay, anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/Gary-Neville-phat-bieu-ve-Marouane-Fellaini-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Fellaini\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Mourinho gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-mu-troi-chan-thanh-cong-fellaini-172-189961.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Fellaini</span>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y b\u1edfi t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf M.U. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng M.U d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ebfn Mourinho v\u00ec ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gary Neville \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Mourinho</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fellaini vd Brighton\" title=\"Fellaini vd Brighton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/5/fel.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville tin Mourinho s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t khi gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Fellaini\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi Mourinho, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Fellaini kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi M.U. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cFellaini r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Fellaini. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"735","checkdouble":"189984"},{"date":"10:49 30/06","title":"Morata CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/morata-chinh-thuc-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alvaro Morata b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 2017, Chelsea b\u1ecf ra 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata t\u1eeb Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n, Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n, Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/morata-chinh-thuc-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Morata v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh tranh ch\u1ea5p k\u00e9m v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Morata ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf NHA.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Giroud v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua t\u1eeb Arsenal, Morata hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ef1u sao Real, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-chelsea-172-185574.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Morata</span>, PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992. Ph\u00eda Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morata \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n, Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n, Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/16/morata-se-la-tuong-lai-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Chelsa. T\u00f4i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp. Sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cQu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u1eaft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay Conte, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"734","checkdouble":"189985"},{"date":"09:36 30/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7): Tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/30/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean khai h\u1ecfa nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn World Cup 2018, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng. \u0110\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 tr\u00f4ng c\u1ea3 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi Uruguay l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p Cavani - Suarez, c\u00f2n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady l\u1edbn v\u00e0o Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 - 17) Tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 - 17) Tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-(1h00---17)-Trong-phao-doi-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 Suarez, Cavani hay Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Cr7 ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u1eefa ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u t\u00e2m\" - HLV Oscar Tabarez chia s\u1ebb trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Ronaldo, Cavani v\u00e0 Suarez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u1edf, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi, sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ed3n b\u00f3ng l\u00ean cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n nay t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi c\u01a1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Uruguay vs Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"Preview Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nUruguay d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Oscar Tabarez kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i gi\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. Trong s\u1ed1 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng th\u00ec hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Uruguay \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0, tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm l\u00e0 khi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng h\u1ebft m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \"Brazil ch\u00e2u \u00c2u\". K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2016 khi l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro b\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ed5i, HLV Fernando Santos v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho Seleccao ch\u01a1i theo phong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00e9m \u0111i s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y toan t\u00ednh. V\u00e0 khi hai k\u1ebb gi\u00e0u toan t\u00ednh g\u1eb7p nhau, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Ch\u1ec9 khi m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i World Cup. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha gi\u1eef th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (1 th\u1eafng, 1 h\u00f2a), l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7/1972 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Maracana (Rio de Janeiro, Brazil) v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong 17 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn (th\u1eafng 8, h\u00f2a 8). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2014. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Seleccao thua c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup (ghi 1, l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u0103m 1986 v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, Uruguay b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i 3 trong 4 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y (1986, 1990 v\u00e0 2014).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1930, Uruguay kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Uruguay ch\u01b0a thua b\u00e0n n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi 6 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m (3 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch). \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u00e0 Brazil n\u0103m 1986.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* C\u1ea3 5 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Uruguay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh (3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, 1 t\u1eeb s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 1 t\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t xa).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Luis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup cho Uruguay, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Osca Miguez (8).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup (424 ph\u00fat)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* N\u1ebfu ra s\u00e2n, Ronaldo s\u1ebd san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup v\u00e0 Euro hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Bastian Schweinsteiger (38).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Uruguay (4-3-1-2): </strong>1.Muslera - 22.Caceres, 2.Gimenez, 3.Godin, 17.Laxalt - 8.Nandez, 14.Torreira, 15.Vecino - 6.Bentancur - 21.Cavani, 9.Suarez</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (4-4-2): </strong>1.Patricio - 21.Cedric, 3.Pepe, 6.Fonte, 5.Guerreiro - 20.Quaresma, 14.W.Carvalho, 8.Moutinho, 10.J.Mario - 9.A.Silva, 7.Ronaldo</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: </strong>Uruguay 0-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Uruguay vs Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-(4-3-1-2-vs-4-4-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\">Suarez nh\u1eafn Ronaldo: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\">Uruguay kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-vui-dap-nga-man-trinh-dien-an-tuong-cua-nhung-hang-hot-421-189571.html\">Uruguay v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Nga: M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-la-loi-canh-tinh-voi-bo-dao-nha-421-189878.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/dt-iran-roi-world-cup-2018-khi-phu-nu-duoc-phep-vao-san-465-189629.html\">\u0110T Iran r\u1eddi World Cup 2018: Khi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p v\u00e0o s\u00e2n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-vat-va-vuot-qua-vong-bang-run-ray-cung-cr7-421-189582.html\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: Run r\u1ea9y c\u00f9ng CR7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"733","checkdouble":"189986"}]}